node.text:
Ok so this is finally the video I promised you guys 10000000 years ago, well, even though this is a sponsored video, I need to tell ya’ll that I read the ingredients and try it out and really like it before actually decided to work with @hairburstvietnam I mean, watch the videos for why I use it and thank you so much for the looooonnnngggg wait bbies also, tell m what do you wanna see next cause making this video was a blast💪🏼💪🏼💪🏼💪🏼 @hairburstvietnam 
#hairburstvietnam #hairgoals #chamsoctoc

Aaaandd I got the gel from @jfirstsaigon dm them for more infos! The gel called Milbon wet shine gel cream 5 btw ;)
